OBJECT Report 16511 Form 27Q
{
  OBJECT-PROPERTIES
  {
    Date=03-08-16;
    Time=12:00:00 PM;
    Version List=NAVIN9.00.00.46621;
  }
  PROPERTIES
  {
    CaptionML=[ENU=Form 27Q;
               ENN=Form 27Q];
    OnPreReport=VAR
                  Form26Q27QEntry@1500001 : Record 16505;
                  ChallanRegister@1500000 : Record 16504;
                  UpdateChallanDetails@1500003 : Report 13721;
                BEGIN
                  CompanyInfo.GET;
                  IF Quar = 0 THEN
                    ERROR(Text16500);
                  IF FinYr = '' THEN
                    ERROR(Text16501);
                  IF TANloc = '' THEN
                    ERROR(Text16502);
                  IF PersonName = '' THEN
                    ERROR(Text16503);
                  IF Designation = '' THEN
                    ERROR(Text16504);
                  IF Date = 0D THEN
                    ERROR(Text16505);
                  IF PANNo = '' THEN
                    ERROR(PANNoEmptyErr);
                  IF CompanyInfo."Phone No." = '' THEN
                    ERROR(CompInfoPhoneNoEmptyErr);
                  IF CompanyInfo."E-Mail" = '' THEN
                    ERROR(CompInfoEmailEmptyErr);
                  IF CompanyInfo."Location Code" = '' THEN
                    ERROR(CompInfoLocationEmptyErr);
                  IF CompanyInfo.Address = '' THEN
                    ERROR(CompInfoAddressEmptyErr);

                  UpdateChallanDetails.UpdateNilChallanEntries(TANloc,Quar,FinYr,FALSE);

                  ChallanRegister.RESET;
                  ChallanRegister.SETRANGE("Financial Year",FinYr);
                  IF NOT ChallanRegister.FINDFIRST THEN
                    ERROR(Text16506,'Financial Year');
                  ChallanRegister.SETRANGE(Quarter,Quar);
                  IF NOT ChallanRegister.FINDFIRST THEN
                    ERROR(Text16506,'Quarter');
                  IF ChallanRegister.FINDFIRST THEN
                    REPEAT
                      IF (ChallanRegister."Challan No." = '') OR ((ChallanRegister."BSR Code" = '') AND
                                                                  (CompanyInfo."Company Status" <>
                                                                   CompanyInfo."Company Status"::Government) AND
                        NOT ChallanRegister."Nil Challan Indicator")
                      THEN
                        ERROR(Text16508);
                      Form26Q27QEntry.RESET;
                      Form26Q27QEntry.SETRANGE("Financial Year",FinYr);
                      IF NOT Form26Q27QEntry.FINDFIRST THEN
                        ERROR(Text16506,'Financial Year');
                      Form26Q27QEntry.SETRANGE(Quarter,Quar);
                      IF NOT Form26Q27QEntry.FINDFIRST THEN
                        ERROR(Text16506,'Quarter');
                      Form26Q27QEntry.SETRANGE("Form No.",Form26Q27QEntry."Form No."::"27Q");
                      IF NOT Form26Q27QEntry.FINDFIRST THEN
                        ERROR(Text16507);
                      Form26Q27QEntry.SETRANGE("T.A.N. No.",TANloc);
                      IF NOT Form26Q27QEntry.FINDFIRST THEN
                        ERROR(Text16506,'T.A.N No.');
                      Form26Q27QEntry.SETRANGE(Printed,TRUE);
                      Form26Q27QEntry.SETRANGE("Challan Register Entry No.",ChallanRegister."Entry No.");
                       Execute += Form26Q27QEntry.COUNT;
                    UNTIL ChallanRegister.NEXT=0;

                  IF (CompanyInfo."Company Status" <> CompanyInfo."Company Status"::Government) AND
                    (STRLEN(MobileNo) <> 10)
                  THEN
                    ERROR(Text16520);
                END;

  }
  DATASET
  {
    { 9960;    ;DataItem;                    ;
               DataItemTable=Table16503;
               DataItemTableView=SORTING(Entry No.)
                                 ORDER(Ascending)
                                 WHERE(Form No.=FILTER(27Q));
               OnPreDataItem=BEGIN
                               SETRANGE("Financial Year",FinYr);
                               SETRANGE(Quarter,Quar);
                               SETRANGE("Form No.","Form No."::"27Q");
                               SETRANGE("Deductor T.A.N. No.",TANloc);
                             END;

               OnAfterGetRecord=BEGIN
                                  IF Quarter = Quarter::Q4 THEN
                                    Year := COPYSTR(FORMAT("Assessment Year"),1,4)
                                  ELSE
                                    Year := COPYSTR(FORMAT("Financial Year"),1,4);

                                  IF Quar = Quar::Q1 THEN
                                    Text := Text16509
                                  ELSE
                                    IF Quar = Quar::Q2 THEN
                                      Text := Text16510
                                    ELSE
                                      IF Quar = Quar::Q3 THEN
                                        Text := Text16511
                                      ELSE
                                        IF Quar = Quar::Q4 THEN
                                          Text := Text16512;

                                  State.SETFILTER("State Code for eTDS/TCS","Batch Header"."Deductor State");
                                    IF State.FINDFIRST THEN
                                      statevar := State.Description;

                                  DedType := "Deductor Category";
                                  DeductorCategory.GET("Deductor Category");

                                  IfFiled := Text16515;
                                  IF "Original RRR No." <> '' THEN
                                    IfFiled := Text16516;

                                  Num := 0;
                                  ChallanRegisterEntryNo := 0;
                                END;
                                 }

    { 1659;2   ;Column  ;Challan_Register_Entry_No_;
               SourceExpr="Entry No." }

    { 8695;2   ;Column  ;Challan_Register_Quarter;
               SourceExpr=Quarter }

    { 3384;2   ;Column  ;Challan_Register_Financial_Year;
               SourceExpr="Financial Year" }

    { 6267;1   ;DataItem;                    ;
               DataItemTable=Table16505;
               DataItemTableView=SORTING(Challan Register Entry No.)
                                 WHERE(Challan Register Entry No.=FILTER(<>0),
                                       Form No.=FILTER(27Q));
               OnPreDataItem=BEGIN
                               CurrReport.CREATETOTALS("Total TDS Including SHE CESS","TDS Amount",TotalTaxDeducted,"eCESS Amount","SHE Cess Amount",
                                 "Surcharge Amount");
                               SETRANGE("Financial Year",FinYr);
                               SETRANGE(Quarter,Quar);
                               SETRANGE("T.A.N. No.",TANloc);
                             END;

               OnAfterGetRecord=BEGIN
                                  NODNOCCertificateNo."Acknowledgement No. (15CA)" := '';
                                  CertificateNo := '';
                                  Printed := TRUE;
                                  MODIFY;

                                  IF ChallanRegisterEntryNo <> "Challan Register Entry No." THEN BEGIN
                                    TotalTaxDepo := 0;
                                    Form26Q27QEntry.RESET;
                                    Form26Q27QEntry.SETRANGE("Challan Register Entry No.","Challan Register Entry No.");
                                    IF Form26Q27QEntry.FINDSET THEN
                                      REPEAT
                                        TotalTaxDepo += Form26Q27QEntry."Total TDS Including SHE CESS";
                                      UNTIL Form26Q27QEntry.NEXT = 0;

                                    IF Quar > 0 THEN BEGIN
                                      TDSAccountingPeriod.SETRANGE("Financial Year for eTDS/TCS",FinYr);
                                        IF TDSAccountingPeriod.FINDFIRST THEN
                                          TDSSetup.RESET;
                                          TDSSetup.SETRANGE("No.",TDSAccountingPeriod."No.");
                                          TDSSetup.SETRANGE(Quarter,Quar);
                                          IF TDSSetup.FINDFIRST THEN BEGIN
                                            EndDate := COPYSTR(FORMAT(TDSSetup."Ending Date"),1,6);
                                            EndDate1 := COPYSTR(FORMAT(TDSSetup."Ending Date"),7,8);
                                          END;
                                    END;

                                    Num2 := 0;
                                    InvAmt := 0;

                                    "Challan Register".SETRANGE("Challan No.","Challan No.");
                                    IF "Challan Register".FINDFIRST THEN BEGIN
                                      "Challan Register".CALCFIELDS("Total TDS Including SHE Cess");
                                      AmountAsPerChallan :=
                                        "Challan Register"."Total TDS Including SHE Cess" + "Challan Register"."Oltas Others" +
                                        "Challan Register"."Oltas Interest" + "Challan Register"."TDS Fee";
                                    END;
                                    ChallanRegisterEntryNo := "Challan Register Entry No.";
                                  END;

                                  Rate := "TDS %" + ("TDS %" * "Surcharge %" / 100);
                                  RateAtWhichDeducted := Rate + (Rate * ("eCESS %" + "SHE Cess %") / 100);

                                  TotalTaxDeducted := ("TDS Amount" + "Surcharge Amount" + "eCESS Amount" + "SHE Cess Amount");

                                  Num2 := Num2 + 1;

                                  IF "Concessional Code" = '' THEN
                                    "Concessional Code" := Text16517;

                                  NODNOCCertificateNo.SETRANGE("No.","Party Code");
                                  NODNOCCertificateNo.SETFILTER("Stating Date",'<=%1',"Posting Date");
                                  NODNOCCertificateNo.SETFILTER("Ending Date",'>=%1',"Posting Date");
                                  IF NODNOCCertificateNo.FINDFIRST THEN
                                    IF ("Concessional Code" = 'A') OR ("Concessional Code" = 'B') THEN
                                      CertificateNo := NODNOCCertificateNo."Certificate No.";
                                  ActApplicable := GetActApplicable;
                                  IF NOT CountryRegion.GET("Country Code") THEN BEGIN
                                    Vendor.GET("Form 26Q/27Q Entry"."Party Code");
                                    CountryRegion.GET(Vendor."Country/Region Code")
                                  END;

                                  InvAmt += ABS("Invoice Amount");

                                  IF Form26Q27QEntry."Deductee Code" = '1' THEN
                                    DedCode := Text16518
                                  ELSE
                                    DedCode := Text16519;
                                END;

               DataItemLink=Quarter=FIELD(Quarter),
                            Financial Year=FIELD(Financial Year) }

                  OnLookup=BEGIN
                             IF Quar > 0 THEN BEGIN
                               TDSSetup.RESET;
                               TDSSetup.SETRANGE(Quarter,Quar);
                               IF TDSSetup.FINDFIRST THEN BEGIN
                                 TDSAccountingPeriod.GET(TDSSetup."No.");
                                 IF PAGE.RUNMODAL(13721,TDSAccountingPeriod) = ACTION::LookupOK THEN
                                   FinYr := TDSAccountingPeriod."Financial Year for eTDS/TCS";
                              END;
                             END;
                           END;
                            }

  <Code>Public Function BlankZero(ByVal Value As Decimal)
    if Value = 0 then
        Return ""
    end if
    Return Value
End Function

Public Function BlankPos(ByVal Value As Decimal)
    if Value &gt; 0 then
        Return ""
    end if
    Return Value
End Function

Public Function BlankZeroAndPos(ByVal Value As Decimal)
    if Value &gt;= 0 then
        Return ""
    end if
    Return Value
End Function

Public Function BlankNeg(ByVal Value As Decimal)
    if Value &lt; 0 then
        Return ""
    end if
    Return Value
End Function

Public Function BlankNegAndZero(ByVal Value As Decimal)
    if Value &lt;= 0 then
        Return ""
    end if
    Return Value
End Function
